msgid "yepi te … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:9.4"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā asayaṅkāraṃ aparaṅkāraṃ adhiccasamuppannaṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti tadapi phassapaccayā. "
msgstr "In the case of those who declare that suffering arises by chance, not made by oneself or another, that’s also conditioned by contact. "

