msgctxt "sn12.24:10.1"
msgid "Tatrānanda, yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā sayaṅkataṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti, te vata aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "In the case of those who declare that suffering is made by oneself, it’s impossible that they will experience that without contact. … "

