msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā asayaṅkāraṃ aparaṅkāraṃ adhiccasamuppannaṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti, te vata aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr "In the case of those who declare that suffering arises by chance, not made by oneself or another, it’s impossible that they will experience that without contact. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc11
msgctxt "sn12.24:11.1"
msgid "Ekamidāhaṃ, ānanda, samayaṃ idheva rājagahe viharāmi veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "Ānanda, this one time I was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:11.2"
msgid "Atha khvāhaṃ, ānanda, pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya rājagahaṃ piṇḍāya pāvisiṃ. "
msgstr "Then I robed up in the morning and, taking my bowl and robe, entered Rājagaha for alms. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:11.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, ānanda, etadahosi: "
msgstr "Then I thought: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:11.4"
msgid "‘atippago kho tāva rājagahe piṇḍāya carituṃ. "
msgstr "‘It’s too early to wander for alms in Rājagaha. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:11.5"
msgid "Yannūnāhaṃ yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkameyyan’ti. "
msgstr "Why don’t I go to the monastery of the wanderers who follow other paths?’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc12
msgctxt "sn12.24:12.1"
msgid "Atha khvāhaṃ, ānanda, yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkamiṃ; upasaṅkamitvā tehi aññatitthiyehi paribbājakehi saddhiṃ sammodiṃ. "
msgstr "Then I went to the monastery of the wanderers who follow other paths, and exchanged greetings with the wanderers there. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:12.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃ. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho maṃ, ānanda, te aññatitthiyā paribbājakā etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, I sat down to one side. …” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.36, sc13
msgctxt "sn12.24:13.1"
msgid "‘Santāvuso gotama, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā sayaṅkataṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti. "
msgstr "(The wanderers asked the Buddha the very same questions, and he gave the same answers.) "

msgctxt "sn12.24:13.2"
msgid "Santi panāvuso gotama, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā paraṅkataṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:13.3"
msgid "Santāvuso gotama, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā sayaṅkatañca paraṅkatañca dukkhaṃ paññapenti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:13.4"
msgid "Santi panāvuso gotama, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā asayaṅkāraṃ aparaṅkāraṃ adhiccasamuppannaṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:13.5"
msgid "Idha no āyasmā gotamo kiṃvādī kimakkhāyī? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:13.6"
msgid "Kathaṃ byākaramānā ca mayaṃ vuttavādino ceva āyasmato gotamassa assāma, na ca āyasmantaṃ gotamaṃ abhūtena abbhācikkheyyāma, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākareyyāma, na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānupāto gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgaccheyyā’ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc14
msgctxt "sn12.24:14.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vuttāhaṃ, ānanda, te aññatitthiye paribbājake etadavocaṃ: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:14.2"
msgid "‘paṭiccasamuppannaṃ kho, āvuso, dukkhaṃ vuttaṃ mayā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:14.3"
msgid "Kiṃ paṭicca? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:14.4"
msgid "Phassaṃ paṭicca. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:14.5"
msgid "Iti vadaṃ vuttavādī ceva me assa, na ca maṃ abhūtena abbhācikkheyya, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākareyya, na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānupāto gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgaccheyyāti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc15
msgctxt "sn12.24:15.1"
msgid "Tatrāvuso, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā sayaṅkataṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti tadapi phassapaccayā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:15.2"
msgid "Yepi te … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:15.3"
msgid "yepi te … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:15.4"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā asayaṅkāraṃ aparaṅkāraṃ adhiccasamuppannaṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti tadapi phassapaccayā. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc16
msgctxt "sn12.24:16.1"
msgid "Tatrāvuso, ye te samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā sayaṅkataṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti, te vata aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:16.2"
msgid "Yepi te … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:16.3"
msgid "yepi te … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn12.24:16.4"
msgid "yepi te samaṇabrāhmaṇā kammavādā asayaṅkāraṃ aparaṅkāraṃ adhiccasamuppannaṃ dukkhaṃ paññapenti, te vata aññatra phassā paṭisaṃvedissantīti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjatī’”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17
msgctxt "sn12.24:17.1"
msgid "“Acchariyaṃ bhante, abbhutaṃ bhante. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, sir, it’s amazing, "

msgctxt "sn12.24:17.2"
msgid "Yatra hi nāma ekena padena sabbo attho vutto bhavissati. "
msgstr "how the whole meaning is stated with one phrase. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:17.3"
msgid "Siyā nu kho, bhante, esevattho vitthārena vuccamāno gambhīro ceva assa gambhīrāvabhāso cā”ti? "
msgstr "Could there be a detailed explanation of this meaning that is both deep and appears deep?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc18
msgctxt "sn12.24:18.1"
msgid "“Tena hānanda, taññevettha paṭibhātū”ti. "
msgstr "“Well then, Ānanda, clarify this matter yourself.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.24:18.2"
msgid "“Sace maṃ, bhante, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "“Sir, suppose they were to ask me: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:18.3"
msgid "‘jarāmaraṇaṃ, āvuso ānanda, kiṃnidānaṃ kiṃsamudayaṃ kiṃjātikaṃ kiṃpabhavan’ti? "
msgstr "‘Reverend Ānanda, what is the source, origin, birthplace, and root of old age and death?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:18.4"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ: "
msgstr "I’d answer like this: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:18.5"
msgid "‘jarāmaraṇaṃ kho, āvuso, jātinidānaṃ jātisamudayaṃ jātijātikaṃ jātipabhavan’ti. "
msgstr "‘Reverends, rebirth is the source, origin, birthplace, and root of old age and death.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:18.6"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ. "
msgstr "That’s how I’d answer such a question. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.37, sc19
msgctxt "sn12.24:19.1"
msgid "Sace maṃ, bhante, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "Suppose they were to ask me: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:19.2"
msgid "‘jāti panāvuso ānanda, kiṃnidānā kiṃsamudayā kiṃjātikā kiṃpabhavā’ti? "
msgstr "‘What is the source of rebirth?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:19.3"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ: "
msgstr "I’d answer like this: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:19.4"
msgid "‘jāti kho, āvuso, bhavanidānā bhavasamudayā bhavajātikā bhavappabhavā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Continued existence is the source of rebirth.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:19.5"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ. "
msgstr "That’s how I’d answer such a question. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc20
msgctxt "sn12.24:20.1"
msgid "Sace maṃ, bhante, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "Suppose they were to ask me: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:20.2"
msgid "‘bhavo panāvuso ānanda, kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo’ti? "
msgstr "‘What is the source of continued existence?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:20.3"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ: "
msgstr "I’d answer like this: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:20.4"
msgid "‘bhavo kho, āvuso, upādānanidāno upādānasamudayo upādānajātiko upādānappabhavo’ti. "
msgstr "‘Grasping is the source of continued existence.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:20.5"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ. "
msgstr "That’s how I’d answer such a question. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc21
msgctxt "sn12.24:21.1"
msgid "Sace maṃ, bhante, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ—"
msgstr "Suppose they were to ask me: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.2"
msgid "upādānaṃ panāvuso … pe … "
msgstr "‘What is the source of grasping?’ … "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.3"
msgid "taṇhā panāvuso … pe … "
msgstr "craving … "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.4"
msgid "vedanā panāvuso … pe … "
msgstr "feeling … "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.5"
msgid "sace maṃ, bhante, evaṃ puccheyyuṃ: "
msgstr "Suppose they were to ask me: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.6"
msgid "‘phasso panāvuso ānanda, kiṃnidāno kiṃsamudayo kiṃjātiko kiṃpabhavo’ti? "
msgstr "‘What is the source of contact?’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.7"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyaṃ: "
msgstr "I’d answer like this: "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.8"
msgid "‘phasso kho, āvuso, saḷāyatananidāno saḷāyatanasamudayo saḷāyatanajātiko saḷāyatanappabhavo’ti. "
msgstr "‘The six sense fields are the source, origin, birthplace, and root of contact.’ "

# NOTE: Note that MS here punctautes correctly; there is a “ti after the previous statement, and at the end of this section. BB omits this detail, which, admittedly, is odd and doesn” t have an immediate explanation.
msgctxt "sn12.24:21.9"
msgid "‘Channaṃ tveva, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā phassanirodho; "
msgstr "‘When the six sense fields fade away and cease with nothing left over, contact ceases. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.10"
msgid "phassanirodhā vedanānirodho; "
msgstr "When contact ceases, feeling ceases. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.11"
msgid "vedanānirodhā taṇhānirodho; "
msgstr "When feeling ceases, craving ceases. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.12"
msgid "taṇhānirodhā upādānanirodho; "
msgstr "When craving ceases, grasping ceases. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.13"
msgid "upādānanirodhā bhavanirodho; "
msgstr "When grasping ceases, continued existence ceases. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.14"
msgid "bhavanirodhā jātinirodho; "
msgstr "When continued existence ceases, rebirth ceases. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.15"
msgid "jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā nirujjhanti. "
msgstr "When rebirth ceases, old age and death, sorrow, lamentation, pain, sadness, and distress cease. "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.16"
msgid "Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī’ti. "
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.’ "

msgctxt "sn12.24:21.17"
msgid "Evaṃ puṭṭhohaṃ, bhante, evaṃ byākareyyan”ti. "
msgstr "That’s how I’d answer such a question.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.24:21.18"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

